IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. CTRLDEMO.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 STATE-FLAG PIC 9 VALUE 0.
   88 IS-DONE VALUE 1.
01 X   PIC S9(4) VALUE -25.
01 IDX PIC 9(3) VALUE 5.
01 ACC PIC 9(4) VALUE 100.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN-PARA.
    PERFORM STEP-A THRU STEP-C.
    SET IS-DONE TO TRUE.
    IF IS-DONE
        DISPLAY "done flag is set"
    END-IF.
    IF X IS NEGATIVE
        DISPLAY "X is negative"
    END-IF.
    SET IDX UP BY 3.
    DISPLAY "idx now " IDX.
    INITIALIZE ACC.
    DISPLAY "acc init " ACC.
    STOP RUN.
STEP-A.
    DISPLAY "step A".
STEP-B.
    DISPLAY "step B".
STEP-C.
    DISPLAY "step C".
